    <div class="er-mt-24 er-space-y-16 mb:er-space-y-8 mb:er-mt-12">
      <section class="er-flex er-flex-col">
        <h3 class="text-size24  mb:er-text-3xl er-font-semibold">Why it feels better</h3>
        <p class="text-size18 mb:er-text-2xl er-font-semibold er-opacity-70 er-mt-2">Smaller, faster, more precise</p>
        <p class="text-size18 mb:er-text-2xl er-opacity-70 er-mt-5">
          The inner rotor spins at a smaller radius with lower inertia, paired with high-ratio precision gears, so
          power kicks in the moment you need it - with no lag and no hesitation.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="er-flex er-flex-col">
        <h3 class="text-size24  mb:er-text-3xl er-font-semibold">Why it's quieter</h3>
        <p class="text-size18 mb:er-text-2xl er-font-semibold er-opacity-70 er-mt-2">More comfort</p>
        <p class="text-size18 mb:er-text-2xl er-opacity-70 er-mt-5">
          All moving parts enclosed in a rigid metal housing lock noise at the source, while high-precision gears
          with minimal profile deviation ensure smooth, vibration-free operation.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="er-flex er-flex-col"> 
        <h3 class="text-size24  mb:er-text-3xl er-font-semibold">Why it's lighter</h3>
        <p class="text-size18 mb:er-text-2xl er-font-semibold er-opacity-70 er-mt-2">More compact by design</p>
        <p class="text-size18 mb:er-text-2xl er-opacity-70 er-mt-5">
          A more integrated structure eliminates bulk, reducing overall weight for a lighter ride.
        </p>
      </section>
    </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</dialog>

<script type="module">

$('button[data-dialog-id="inner-rotor-motor"]').on('click', function () {
    console.log($(this).attr('data-dialog-id'))

    showDialog(document.getElementById($(this).attr('data-dialog-id')))
})
</script>
